H3.text: The Nullarbor Plain is in which country. Straya

A4.text: The Nullarbor Plain is part of the area of flat, almost treeless, arid or semi-arid country of southern Australia.

A5.text: Frequently The Nullarbor is expanded in tourist literature and web-based material to loosely refer to all the land between Adelaide, South Australia and Perth, Western Australia.
